    NPDE Plots

    Kyle Baron

    2018-12-12

    npde_plots.Rmd

    Set up

    library(pmplots)
library(dplyr)

data <- pmplots_data_obs()

    NPDE versus time

    npde_time(data)

    npde_tad(data)

    NPDE versus PRED

    npde_pred(data)

    NPDE histogram

    npde_hist(data)
    ## `stat_bin()` using `bins = 30`. Pick better value with `binwidth`.

    NPDE QQ plot

    npde_q(data)

    NPDE versus categorical variable

    cont_cat(data, x = "STUDYc", y = "NPDE") + pm_hline()

    NPDE versus continuous variables

    cont_cont(data, x= "WT//Weight (kg)", y = "NPDE") + 
  pm_hline() + pm_smooth()
